02:05.174 --> 02:06.372
So, what's the big surprise?

02:06.550 --> 02:09.966
A whole shelf. lt's all for you.

02:10.973 --> 02:12.348
Well, l'm touched.

02:12.516 --> 02:14.425
Well, you said
you needed more room

02:14.602 --> 02:16.927
and l kind of like the idea
of your books in my locker.

02:17.731 --> 02:21.350
